	SCO. From RuPaul's Drag Race Season 14\, 2022 and most recently All Stars 
	10 from 2025\, BOSCO is now headlining her first ever solo tour. Meet & Gr
	eet add-on tickets are sold separately. To attend the M&G\, fans must also
	 purchase a ticket to the event. Show starts at 8pm. There will be a 20-mi
	nute intermission. Ages 18+ welcome w/ Valid ID for entry. Check DragFans.
	com and HereIsBosco.com for tour info VIP Tables seat 4 humans and are fir
	st come first serve if you purchase in that section. Please arrive early s
	o that our hosts may seat your party together.\nMurray & Peter Present: "T
	he Marvelous Miss Gender" starring BOSCO. From RuPaul's Drag Race Season 1
	4\, 2022 and most recently All Stars 10 from 2025\, BOSCO is now headlinin
	g her first ever solo tour. Meet & Greet add-on tickets are sold separatel
	y. To attend the M&G\, fans must also purchase a ticket to the event. Show
	 starts at 8pm. There will be a 20-minute intermission. Ages 18+ welcome w
	/ Valid ID for entry. Check DragFans.com and HereIsBosco.com for tour info
	 VIP Tables seat 4 humans and are first come first serve if you purchase i
	n that section. Please arrive early so that our hosts may seat your party 
	together.\n\nhttps://www.ticketmaster.com/the-marvelous-miss-gender-starri
	ng-bosco-houston-texas-07-22-2026/event/3A006469C4B6C4C8\n\nFrom House of 
